# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally committed so the package works when installed
# straight from GitHub (`pnpm add github:tmyuu/emdash-stripe`).
# A `prepare` script rebuilds it on git installs where lifecycle scripts run;
# the committed copy is the fallback for environments that block them.
